events.message: travis: Print memory and number of cpus

events.body:
For [this build](https://travis-ci.org/bitcoin/bitcoin/builds/562357731) I'm seeing:
```bash
ARM - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
Win64 - Number of CPUs (nproc): 1
Dash - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 1
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 1
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
Linux - Number of CPUs (nproc): 2
MacOS - Number of CPUs (nproc): 1
```
Going to merge this to see how much the numbers fluctuate in other pull requests
